title: Ambrosia Cafe
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Small, American-run cafe next to the White Rose. Offers a tofu burger, tofu and chips, a couple Khmer dishes that substitute tofu for the meat, a couple of veggie wraps, and also salads. Owner knows what vegan means, and menu is in English. Specific items that contain no animal ingredients are listed as such on the menu.
